headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Vehicle Discounts
content:
There is a veritable fleet of vehicles on sale this week. Get the MTL Wastelander at 60% off. Or take 50% off the Nagasaki Blazer Aqua. You can also purchase the Emperor Vectre for 30% off through January 26.

Additionally, find 40% off the below Vehicles:

- HVY Barrage
- Progen Itali GTB/GTB Custom
- Invetero Coquette D10
- JoBuilt Hauler Custom

And More! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
